Ground Rules

  No scope creep past v1.0 minimum. If it's not on this list, it
    waits.
  Every coordinate-pipeline change tested on physical iPad before
    marking done.
  Pressure → render path also tested on iPad before marking done.
  Selection tools: scale/rotate handles are deferred to v1.1. Ship
    marquee + lasso + delete + copy-to-layer.
  When fixing UX surfaces, propose ONE minimal change at a time.
    Don't stack modifiers (added Apr 16 after the keyboard fix had to
    be reverted).
  Document every fix here with root cause and sim-verified vs.
    iPad-retest annotation.


